lemma fun_prod_commute: assumes "f 1 = 1" and "\<And>x y. f (x * y) = f x * f y" shows "f (prod g A) = (\<Prod>a\<in>A. f (g a))"
by (induct A rule: infinite_finite_induct) (simp_all add: assms diff_mult_distrib)
